---
<MainLayout>
	<div class="p-6 lg:p-6 grid gap-8 place-items-center h-screen content-center w-full md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 xl:w-1/3 mx-auto">
		<div class="text-center">
			<img class="w-48 h-48 mb-6 drop-shadow-xl rounded-full mx-auto" src="https://finishednotes.com/images/kristi%20portrait,%20square-512.webp" loading="lazy" alt="portrait image" width="256" height="256" />
			<h1 class="font-serif italic text-2xl">Dr. Kristi Cash White, PhD, LPC</h1>
			<h2 class="font-bold text-base tracking-widest uppercase">Licensed Counselor</h2>
		</div>
		<p class="font-serif text-xl">
			Dr. Kristi Cash White is an Oregon-licensed counselor and education professional with a Ph.D. in Counseling Education & Supervision from <a href="https://www.ucumberlands.edu/" title="University of the Cumberlands website">University of the Cumberlands</a>. She is an experienced counselor with specialities in play therapy, public speaking, supervising counselors-in-training, and teaching.
		</p>
		<a href="https://kristicashwhitecounseling.clientsecure.me" target="_blank" class="button" title="Start your visit in a new window">Schedule a visit with Kristi</a>
	</div>
</MainLayout>
